fiftyone.mobile.detection.entities

Class Profile

  • java.lang.Object
    • fiftyone.mobile.detection.entities.BaseEntity
      • fiftyone.mobile.detection.entities.Profile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Profile>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Profile, Profile

    public abstract class Profile
extends BaseEntity
implements Comparable<Profile>
    Represents a collection of properties and values relating to a profile which in turn relates to a component. Each Signature relates to one profile for each component.
